</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=154.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_lightbulb.gif" align=absmiddle>  Radical Ideas take 2</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>Some Radical Caster/Mage Ideas</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--></i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
Well I have read a ton of threads and decided to toss out some ideas that may be radical to see what people think and to make people think. That is think something other then I'm crazy <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
For now I will toss out the ideas and can elaborate on them further if people wish. Others may of course toss in ideas and variations they think would work also.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> This</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> thread was inspired by all the mages and <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Razamatazz Pizzazz</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
Ok on with the <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>Ideas</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>Spell Stuff</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Make all spells Memorizable by <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> any</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> level Magician/Caster. You may be able to memorize the spell but do not have the fortitued to cast it yet.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Make all spells that are memorized Scribe-able. You scribe the spell and it becomes a spell scroll and is removed from your spellbook. If the spell is Ancient and no drop it can not be scribed.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Add some new spells that can be researched and quested for and not just drops. Maybe have an NPC that you hand the spell components to do the research for you for an extra cost, like another reagent or some plat etc...<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Make a few more of our spells Group friendly. Like Elemental Shield. Allow us to target someone and right click a waterstone on them.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Place some of the new uber spells on merchants for a gooodly amount of money, like 250p as a starter and scaling up to 1-2k or maybe more.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Create some spells with stuff for pets in mind. Examples<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Magi'Kots Pouch of Pet Power: Level 58. Summons one muzzle of mardu type haste item, a dagger that procs a 90pt dd not usable by a pet lower then level 40, a neck item that increases attack by 50 and has 25 ac and an earring with 20 to all resists and 20 ac. Pet Only.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Transon's small stake: Summons a dagger type weapon that procs a 30pt disease dd and gives the pet a 15% move increase. Level 34.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>Mana Regeneration</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Add +1 to all Phantom armor type spells, increasing by +1 per spell. Add +2 more to TPP.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Add 1 charge to mod rod at L44 and a lesser mod rod at 29.<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>Pre Existing Utility Summons</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Let Waterstones Stack<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Add a charge to Levitate rings.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Change every summons we have that is on an existing item for another class so that our summon is better then the item. Examples...<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Magician summoned Bandages now allow you to bind either 10% more hp or heal more &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp hp.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Magician summoned pouch of quellios has the shurikens stats increased by +1 and  summon 6 sets instead of 3<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Magician summoned throwing daggers and arrows get stats added to them.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Magician food can have a minor stat increase added to them +1 to int/wis for food, +1 str/dex for water<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Make Gift of Xev <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> really</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> usefull. Add another set of bandages, 1 mod rod, 1 levi ring and 1 waterstone.  I make these for Dead People <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  and call them Veldin's Care Kit <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Make the 2hb 1hb and add a few charges.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Chage the current weapon summons no one uses so that people will use them. Add scaling level limits if needed.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>Gear</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Add more gear that can be usable off of some more common mobs. Boots of Bladecalling are too rare for many Magicians to see. Make a lesser version and greater version and place on appropriate mobs.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Have this gear have some good effects used to counteract mage weaknesses. Examples<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->A temporary charged <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> hp</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> regeneration item. 10 charges and will recharge to full when empty and you are logged out for 30 min or more. Limits its uses per day without making it another &quot;Oh its out of charges? time to destroy/sell it&quot;<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->A <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> self only</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> teleport spell to an elemental place like lavastorm or skyfire.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->An item that makes a fire nuke check cold resistance instead.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->An item that turns a <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> self only</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> spell into a group spell for 3x the mana cost. Limit it to buff types.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Create an item that lets you cast a spell one circle/spell level/group higher then you currently can.<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Defensive Stuff</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Fast cast, huge hp...<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> and i mean <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> huge</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->, aoe snare, no damage, target hate list raiser pet. Make a variety for levels 20, 30, 40, 50, 56, 60.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Give mages a <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> lesser</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> rune line of spells for that needed gate channeling and more raid/grind assist. Help keep that chanter/cleric alive while pet tries to taunt off them.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>Pets</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Lower pet hold to a general aa skill for pet classes at level 51.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Pets Indifferent to any mob that its not attacking or is attacking the mage.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Increase pets <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> HP and ATT</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> ratings. Maybe up damage by 4-8 pts a hit or so depending on the pet.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Add in some other bonus for using each kind of pet. OR an alternate cast/proc. Examples<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Earth pet bashes and doesn't kick and bashes semi often.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Water pet procs a 20% slow.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Firepets procs a DS on your party.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Airpet procs malosi.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Epic pet procs any of the above randomly and not often.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>Skills</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Create <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Discs</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> for Casters as should have been done in the beginning. Examples<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Disc resists: Lowers a mobs restances to your spells for xxx by 50%<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Disc defense: doubles your effective ac and doubles your fizzle rate on all damage spells<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Disc mana boost: increases mana regen by 5/ tick for xxx.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Disc megapet: increase pets attack / damage alot for xxx, costs xxx mana as a constant.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Increase our <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> bind wounds</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> cap to 175 or 150 so we can naturally bind up to 65% or so.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->Have the Monster Summon line work like Dire Charm. It summons a monster in the zone to be your pet for 30 min then pet suicides, if in combat after that combat. Same restrictions on level as dire charm. Reclaiming pet causes mob to Poof and return the mana you spent.<br>
<br>
<br>
Some of these should be and are off the wall but thats the idea. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Would I implement all of them? Dunno that would all be part of the caster balance.<br>
<br>
Sorry it doesn't look as nice as it could have but lists don't seem to work on this particular ezboard. Defense may get screwed up again and I have no idea why it would<br>
<br>
Veldin Darkfire<br>
Master of the Skittles Stick <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/utarekravnos.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tarek Ravnos</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.myezboard.com/projects/ezboard/ezboard_userimages/legends11114/images/banghead.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 21<br> <font color=#333333>(4/2/02 7:03:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=154.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://pages.sbcglobal.net/paulburke1/Tarek.jpg  HEIGTH=150 WIDTH=150></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_lightbulb.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Radical Ideas take 2</span><hr size=1> Quote: &quot;Pets Indifferent to any mob that its not attacking or is attacking the mage.&quot;<br>
