what?!  are you insane..  this one statement makes me want to throw out the entire list of proposals.<br>
<br>
This list in general is stuff that isn't all that effective...I don't want to be a summoning whore.  You may say &quot;but you picked a summonign class&quot;.  Well bah...  bah I say...  Rogues were supposed to be the shady people of Norrath but all they are to Verant is damage output.  bah<br>
<br>
Not a good list...  at all<br>
